    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I could imagine that we'd need to call <code>lean_inc</code> on the objects that we pass to <code>check_str_impl</code>?<br>\nAt least I assume that <code>check_str_impl</code> will \"drop\" its inputs, and thus call <code>lean_dec</code> on them.</p>",
